<section title="welcome" id="welcome" class="welcome">
  <header  data-theme="light">
    <h2>Welcome</h2>
    <p>West Warwickshire Sports Complex (WWSC) is in the heart of Solihull and welcomes members and the public to enjoy our great multi-sports and hospitality facility. We can trace the roots of WWSC back to 1888 with Olton & West Warwicks Cricket Club and 1898 with Olton & West Warwicks Hockey Club. WWSC has been an established charity since 2005 with the objective of providing the best multi-sports facility to the local community. </p>
    <section class="cto">
      <form action="/join">
        <button>membership</button>
      </form>
      <form action="/contact">
        <button>book a tour</button>
      </form>
      <form action="/opening-times">
        <button>opening times</button>
      </form>
      <form action>
        <button><a href="{{bookNow}}" target="_blank">book a session</a></button>
      </form>

    </section>
  </header>
  <section title="aerial-video" id="aerial-video" class="aerial-video">
    <video controls>
      

      <source src="https://videos.ctfassets.net/ffrbyg3cfykl/2JFdc3PK3y2JllOM1b4qaL/806e87c1a2a553b1037000614e7d7935/wwsc-video.webm" type="video/webm">      
      
